@caption Empty Portfolio
The portfolio allows you to keep track of different securities that you own 
and monitor their performance. There are two ways you can get started with
the worksheet. You can import your broker's statement (the list of your 
transactions into AST by clicking on the 'Import Brokers Statement' link 
on the left. You can also click on the 'Add Security' link to add a single 
security to your portfolio.
